claim.claim-text:
1. A hydroxypolyamide product comprising, a hydroxypolyamide component and a salt component, each component produced in the same polymerization process,
wherein the hydroxypolyamide component is derived from at least one esterified polyacid and polyamine salt;
wherein the at least one esterified polyacid and polyamine salt is derived from at least one polyacid:polyamine salt;
wherein the at least one polyacid:polyamine salt is derived from at least one polyacid and at least one polyamine;
wherein the at least one polyacid is derived from at least one organic polyacid having at least one pendant hydroxyl group;
wherein the at least one polyamine is derived from at least one organic polyamine; and
wherein the polymerization process includes treating the esterified polyacid and polyamine salt with a base stronger than a tertiary amine;
wherein the minimum concentration (wgt/vol %) of the hydroxypolyamide product required to form a gel in solution is ≦0.75%.

8. A gel comprising a hydroxypolyamide product and a liquid component,
wherein the hydroxypolyamide product comprises a hydroxypolyamide component and a salt component, each component produced in the same polymerization process;
wherein the hydroxypolyamide component is derived from at least one esterified polyacid and polyamine salt;
wherein the at least one esterified polyacid and polyamine salt is derived from at least one polyacid:polyamine salt;
wherein the at least one polyacid:polyamine salt is derived from at least one polyacid and at least one polyamine;
wherein the at least one polyacid is derived from at least one organic polyacid having at least one pendant hydroxyl group;
wherein the at least one polyamine is derived from at least one organic polyamine; and
wherein the polymerization process includes treating the esterified polyacid and polyamine salt with a base stronger than a tertiary amine;
wherein the minimum concentration (wgt/vol %) of the hydroxypolyamide product required to form a gel in solution is ≦0.75%.

22. A gel forming agent comprising at least one hydroxypolyamide product comprising a hydroxypolyamide component and a salt component, each component produced in the same polymerization process,
wherein the hydroxypolyamide component is derived from at least one esterified polyacid and polyamine salt;
wherein the at least one esterified polyacid and polyamine salt is derived from at least one polyacid:polyamine salt;
wherein the at least one polyacid:polyamine salt is derived from at least one polyacid and at least one polyamine;
wherein the at least one polyacid is derived from at least one organic polyacid having at least one pendant hydroxyl group;
wherein the at least one polyamine is derived from at least one organic polyamine; and
wherein the polymerization process includes treating the esterified polyacid and polyamine salt with a base stronger than a tertiary amine;
wherein the minimum concentration (wgt/vol %) of the hydroxypolyamide product required to form a gel in solution is ≦0.75%.
